          },
          "reviewBody": "I had the opportunity to experience Rawal International School, and overall, I am impressed with the quality of education and support provided. The school offers a well-rounded curriculum that balances academics, extracurricular activities, and personal development.\n\nAcademics\nThe teaching staff is knowledgeable and dedicated, ensuring students understand the material. The school promotes critical thinking and problem-solving, with a variety of courses tailored to different student needs and interests.\n\nFacilities\nThe campus is well-maintained, with modern facilities that support learning and extracurricular activities. Classrooms are equipped with the latest technology, and there are ample resources in libraries and labs for hands-on learning.\n\nExtracurriculars\nThere are numerous clubs and activities available for students to explore their passions outside the classroom. From sports teams to arts programs, the school fosters an environment where students can grow holistically.\n\nStudent Support\nThe school provides robust support systems, including guidance counselors and mentorship programs. Mental health resources are also available, which is crucial for student well-being.\n\nOverall Experience\nRawal International School is a great environment for academic and personal growth. The sense of community, coupled with strong educational programs, makes it a solid choice for students seeking a comprehensive school experience.",
